Boto does not correctly populate the request parameter for suppressing a mapping

EC2 expected syntax: {{BlockDeviceMapping.n.NoDevice}}
Syntax used by boto: {{BlockDeviceMapping.Ebs.n.NoDevice}}

Filed a bug here: https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=906929 
And submitted a pull request: https://github.com/boto/boto/pull/1290
